{
  "_note": "Catalogue of every Mermaid diagram type this skill can produce. 'tier' = dhl_core (styled, builder-backed, DHL colour scheme) or plain (official syntax, no DHL styling). 'doc' is the bundled official syntax reference under references/mermaid-syntax/. Builder-backed core types should be generated with scripts/mermaid_builder.py + validated with scripts/validate_mermaid.py; plain types are hand-written from their doc.",
